        <p>When adding a new file to a project, you can now associate file tags with that file. In the Add File dialog, expand the <span class="Emphasis">Attributes</span> area at the bottom. Then next to the <span class="Emphasis">File Tags</span> field, click <img src="../../../../Images/browse_ellipses.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> and select the relevant file tags.<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive"> See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Interface/UI_Elements/Add_File_Dialog.htm">Add File Dialog</MadCap:xref>, <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../File_Tagging/About_File_Tagging.htm">About File Tagging</MadCap:xref>, and <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../File_Tagging/Associating_Tags_with_Files.htm">Associating Tags with Files</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
